  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Home Deception</h2>A teen's grandma got sick, but his mother couldn't go take care of her, so he did. It turns out that taking care of her <strong>is the least of his worries</strong>, though.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163910/extras/c861e8b83e233873a9cd65735dec078b.poster.avif?t=1736701162\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163910/extras/c861e8b83e233873a9cd65735dec078b.webm?t=1736701162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163910/extras/c861e8b83e233873a9cd65735dec078b.mp4?t=1736701162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Home Deception is a short game based on the <strong>psychological horror</strong> of a situation that simulates real life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>This game includes an immersive experience made by the conversation, computer, walking and more mechanics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">· Realistic Atmosphere</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">· Conversations with NPCs </ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">· Computer Mechanic </ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Home Deception</h2>A teen's grandma got sick, but his mother couldn't go take care of her, so he did. It turns out that taking care of her <strong>is the least of his worries</strong>, though.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163910/extras/c861e8b83e233873a9cd65735dec078b.poster.avif?t=1736701162\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163910/extras/c861e8b83e233873a9cd65735dec078b.webm?t=1736701162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163910/extras/c861e8b83e233873a9cd65735dec078b.mp4?t=1736701162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Home Deception is a short game based on the <strong>psychological horror</strong> of a situation that simulates real life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>This game includes an immersive experience made by the conversation, computer, walking and more mechanics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">· Realistic Atmosphere</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">· Conversations with NPCs </ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">· Computer Mechanic </ul>",
